# make-aggrid

[![PyPI version](https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/make-aggrid.svg)](https://pypi.org/project/make-aggrid/)
[![Python versions](https://img.shields.io/pypi/pyversions/make-aggrid.svg)](https://pypi.org/project/make-aggrid/)
